Variety’s Power Of Women event held at Cipriani Midtown on April 05, 2019 in New York City. The star-studded event was attended by Taraji P. Henson, Yara Shahidi, Gigi Hadid, Julianne Moore, Christiane Amanpour, Bette Midler, Jimmy Fallon, Ashley Graham, Bella Hadid and more. Taraji P. Henson was an honoree at the event and during her tearful speech, she discussed one of the things she’s most passionate about – mental health – and its effect on the black community. See the photos below.